{"tid":1927751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【眾籌：美國人口普查要人！】召喚所有人 要推到美國啲姨媽姑姐都見到！","createTime":"2020-03-16T03:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T06:11:50.000Z","uid":151544,"like":11,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"916ead90763bc74673fd7603c54b94de0f5ef4e7","tid":1927751,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"【眾籌：美國人口普查要人！】召喚所有人 要推到美國啲姨媽姑姐都見到！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1926928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1926928</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n個post已經推唔到，所以幫手開返個新post ,幫吓海外手足，同埋唔好只推唔做，減輕海外負擔"},{"pid":"390782e36e9c1a99783b31799b89bded1727631c","tid":1927751,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a39a7184ad38f5ceb6d51d22a7c26e8850f063f5","tid":1927751,"uid":151544,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:37:45.000Z","msg":"#1<br />\n麻雀妹<br />\n&bull; 15h<br />\n大家好，我係麻雀妹Frances Hui，當武漢肺炎喺全球肆虐，害到美國都死死下停哂課，但我哋唔會停！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aDqMJGXupn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaDqMJGXupn4&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=876548ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aDqMJGXupn4</a> <br />\n<br />\n2020年，又到咗美國十年一度嘅大型人口普查，\u001c聽落去好似無乜特別，但其實同香港人有好大關係！就算你無美國passport，過咗去讀書都規定係要參加！今年已經係美國歷史以來第23次嘅人口普查，但到今時今日亞洲一欄下仍然無「台灣人」同「香港人」呢兩個選項[/5ed]，台灣人嘅數字依然被政府列喺中國人嘅類別中，而香港人就直頭無數據，[red]直接被加入去中國人個數字。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然係咁，台灣人喺過去四次普查都不斷咁呼籲自己友填返台灣人，最後喺上次2010年嘅普查中，由2000年嘅十幾萬人升咗65%去二十幾萬。當我同台灣朋友講，香港人無人搞呢啲campaign時，佢哋都好驚訝。<br />\n<br />\n所以今次，到香港人啦！呢個Campaign好簡單叫做 U.S. 2020 Census: Write in Hongkonger 2020人口普查：我係香港人，係由新組織We The Hongkongers發起（背景唔多講自己睇），希望叫所有居美港人剔番「其他亞裔」一欄，再寫番「香港人Hongkonger」上去。<br />\n<br />\n喺未來呢兩三個月，我哋會喺不同嘅網絡平台落廣告，包括Facebook, YouTube, Google，亦會去社區中心、餐廳呢啲多港人聚首嘅地方宣傳。我哋會製作一套文宣同產品，已經拜託不同美國城市幫手，喺佢哋嘅城市到派文宣，同時與不同團體洽商搵贊助。喺咁短時間內要execute成個marketing嘅campaign，係需要大量嘅資金去支持，所以我哋成立咗一個GoFundMe，希望可以眾籌到最少$60000美金去繼續籌備落去。我哋嘅目標並唔係一班美國手足，而係嗰啲一直有大中華意識、喺香港移民過美國嘅人，要佢哋知道，其實佢都可以寫番自己係香港人。我哋唔奢望喺最後份報告上面，香港人唔會再喺中國嗰個分類下，但我哋好希望可以有香港人嘅一個數字，代表我哋存在喺呢個國家入面。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n個普查其實已經開始咗，陸陸續續有人收到填寫嘅詳情，仲有啲人心急填咗，點知又填錯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。所以呢個Project真係得緊急，好需要大家幫手。大家可以以個人或組織名義去捐錢，而我哋為了答謝你哋嘅貢獻，將會將你寫嘅名稱紀錄在我們的活動網站，分不同嘅級別去列舉。<br />\n<br />\n詳情請睇：<br />\n眾籌網址：<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/us-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fus-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=a1e9ec84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/us-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger</a><br />\n眾籌網址：<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/us-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fus-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=a1e9ec84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/us-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger</a><br />\n眾籌網址：<a href=\"https://www.gofundme.com/f/us-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gofundme.com%2Ff%2Fus-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=a1e9ec84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gofundme.com/f/us-2020-census-write-in-hongkonger</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你無錢，唔緊要！麻煩你哋幫手喺Facebook同YouTube share下條宣傳片<br />\n(facebook: <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wethehongkongers/videos/549389139015795/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwethehongkongers%2Fvideos%2F549389139015795%2F&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=62bd20b2\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/wethehongkongers/videos/549389139015795/</a> ) ，等多啲人知道我哋係可以填香港人。<br />\n如果你有與趣去幫喺呢個camapaign，你亦可以去 <a href=\"http://www.wethehongkongers.org/campaign-work \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wethehongkongers.org%2Fcampaign-work%20&d=ly5XvLwGuIZ6JSW2uqe%2Bvrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=dfadcbdc\" target=\"_blank\">www.wethehongkongers.org/campaign-work </a> 上填寫表格。<br />\n<br />\n最後，如果你係喺美國，無論你係咩公民，你都有權力同責任去填寫呢份Form，所以留學生都要出動啊！"},{"pid":"68ca5ff19c3b12579276bb13b937ab5180d3f85c","tid":1927751,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd695ab15fc0fbc1f116b126b87bebeeaeadf7d","tid":1927751,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"390782e36e9c1a99783b31799b89bded1727631c","tid":1927751,"uid":151544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99743e134237bab30350339212c3d6f7e5d19a6d","tid":1927751,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-16T03:40:08.000Z"